page.title: 17My Day
page.content: My typical school day starts when I get up and get changed into my school clothes.When I am dressed I go and have a wash.After washing I to downstairs and have my breakfast which consists of cornflakes and coffee.After I have eaten my breakfast I make my packed lunch. I live about two miles away from the school and it takes me 45 minutes to get there.School starts at 9.00am and finishes at 3.30pm and we have one and a half hours at lunch break. During the evening I usually go digging for old bottles in the creek. (They used the creeks to dump rubbish).Sometimes I stay in and play games on my computer. At about 9.00pm I get my supper then about 10.00pm I go to bed. Scott Hanson.
